CMD_Element.name: abstract
CMD_Element.Documentation: A summary of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: accessRights
CMD_Element.Documentation: Information about who can access the resource or an indication of its security status.

CMD_Element.name: accrualMethod
CMD_Element.Documentation: The method by which items are added to a collection.

CMD_Element.name: accrualPeriodicity
CMD_Element.Documentation: The frequency with which items are added to a collection.

CMD_Element.name: accrualPolicy
CMD_Element.Documentation: The policy governing the addition of items to a collection.

CMD_Element.name: alternative
CMD_Element.Documentation: An alternative name for the resource.

CMD_Element.name: audience
CMD_Element.Documentation: A class of entity for whom the resource is intended or useful.

CMD_Element.name: available
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date (often a range) that the resource became or will become available.

CMD_Element.name: bibliographicCitation
CMD_Element.Documentation: A bibliographic reference for the resource.

CMD_Element.name: conformsTo
CMD_Element.Documentation: An established standard to which the described resource conforms.

CMD_Element.name: contributor
CMD_Element.Documentation: An entity responsible for making contributions to the resource.

CMD_Element.name: coverage
CMD_Element.Documentation: The spatial or temporal topic of the resource, the spatial applicability of the resource, or the jurisdiction under which the resource is relevant.

CMD_Element.name: created
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date of creation of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: creator
CMD_Element.Documentation: An entity primarily responsible for making the resource.

CMD_Element.name: date
CMD_Element.Documentation: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: dateAccepted
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date of acceptance of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: dateCopyrighted
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date of copyright.

CMD_Element.name: dateSubmitted
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date of submission of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: description
CMD_Element.Documentation: An account of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: educationLevel
CMD_Element.Documentation: A class of entity, defined in terms of progression through an educational or training context, for which the described resource is intended.

CMD_Element.name: extent
CMD_Element.Documentation: The size or duration of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: format
CMD_Element.Documentation: The file format, physical medium, or dimensions of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: hasFormat
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is substantially the same as the pre-existing described resource, but in another format.

CMD_Element.name: hasPart
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is included either physically or logically in the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: hasVersion
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is a version, edition, or adaptation of the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: identifier
CMD_Element.Documentation: An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.

CMD_Element.name: instructionalMethod
CMD_Element.Documentation: A process, used to engender knowledge, attitudes and skills, that the described resource is designed to support.

CMD_Element.name: isFormatOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is substantially the same as the described resource, but in another format.

CMD_Element.name: isPartOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource in which the described resource is physically or logically included.

CMD_Element.name: isReferencedBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that references, cites, or otherwise points to the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: isReplacedBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that supplants, displaces, or supersedes the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: isRequiredBy
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that requires the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

CMD_Element.name: issued
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date of formal issuance (e.g., publication) of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: isVersionOf
CMD_Element.Documentation: Changes in version imply substantive changes in content rather than differences in format.

CMD_Element.name: language
CMD_Element.Documentation: A language of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: license
CMD_Element.Documentation: A legal document giving official permission to do something with the resource.

CMD_Element.name: mediator
CMD_Element.Documentation: An entity that mediates access to the resource and for whom the resource is intended or useful.

CMD_Element.name: medium
CMD_Element.Documentation: The material or physical carrier of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: modified
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date on which the resource was changed.

CMD_Element.name: provenance
CMD_Element.Documentation: A statement of any changes in ownership and custody of the resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.

CMD_Element.name: publisher
CMD_Element.Documentation: An entity responsible for making the resource available.

CMD_Element.name: references
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is referenced, cited, or otherwise pointed to by the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: relation
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource.

CMD_Element.name: replaces
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is supplanted, displaced, or superseded by the described resource.

CMD_Element.name: requires
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource that is required by the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

CMD_Element.name: rights
CMD_Element.Documentation: Information about rights held in and over the resource.

CMD_Element.name: rightsHolder
CMD_Element.Documentation: A person or organization owning or managing rights over the resource.

CMD_Element.name: source
CMD_Element.Documentation: A related resource from which the described resource is derived.

CMD_Element.name: spatial
CMD_Element.Documentation: Spatial characteristics of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: subject
CMD_Element.Documentation: The topic of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: tableOfContents
CMD_Element.Documentation: A list of subunits of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: temporal
CMD_Element.Documentation: Temporal characteristics of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: title
CMD_Element.Documentation: A name given to the resource.

CMD_Element.name: type
CMD_Element.Documentation: The nature or genre of the resource.

CMD_Element.name: valid
CMD_Element.Documentation: Date (often a range) of validity of a resource.

CMD_Element.name: description
CMD_Element.Documentation: Provides the description of the resource in prose

CMD_Element.name: restrictionsOfUse
CMD_Element.Documentation: mandatory if availability=="available-restrictedUse"

CMD_Element.name: distributionAccessMedium
CMD_Element.Documentation: Specifies the medium (channel) used for delivery or providing access to the resource

CMD_Element.name: surname
CMD_Element.Documentation: The surname (family name) of a person related to the resource

CMD_Element.name: givenName
CMD_Element.Documentation: The given name (first name) of a person related to the resource; initials can also be used

CMD_Element.name: organizationName
CMD_Element.Documentation: The full name of an organization

CMD_Element.name: metadataCreationDate
CMD_Element.Documentation: The date of creation of this metadata description

CMD_Element.name: validated
CMD_Element.Documentation: Specifies the validation status of the resource

CMD_Element.name: samplesLocation
CMD_Element.Documentation: A url with samples of the resource or, in the case of tools, of samples of the output

CMD_Element.name: fundingType
CMD_Element.Documentation: Specifies the type of funding of the project
